## ğŸ§® Algorithm
1. Start program  
2. Accept target input  
3. Resolve hostname to IP  
4. Accept port range  
5. For each port:  
   - Create TCP socket  
   - Attempt connection  
   - If successful, mark port as open  
6. Display results  
7. End program  

